3
. Maintaining Normal Operation of Basic Functions, Network and Operational Security
When you use Print Master's App, in order to ensure your normal use of our services, to maintain the normal operation of our services, to improve and optimise our service experience, and to protect your account security, we will collect your operation logs, service logs (network request information, operation paths, exception information, Bluetooth connection of the device and print interaction logs, interaction parameters, SDK initialisation) information so that we can analyse and troubleshoot the causes of user malfunctions. ) so that we can analyse and troubleshoot the causes of user failures.
1.
4
. Customer Service
When you contact us, you can describe the problem by uploading a picture or video, which requires access to your camera or photo album; feedback problems can be uploaded with a picture, which requires access to your camera or photo album in order to provide you with customer service. Our customer service will use your account information to verify your identity with you. You may be asked to provide information in addition to that given above when communicating with our customer service staff. Failure to do so will not affect your ability to use other features and services of this product.
